Want to buy electric vehicle (EV)? Already own one? This app will help to know everything about EV and compare with ICEV:
- Initial costs;
- Running costs; 
- Cost of 1 km / mile; 
- Potential driving range; 
- Actual driving range; 
- Full period costs; 
- Net result of owning EV.
And all this could be compared with any ICEV. Save as many EVs and ICEVs as you wish, open analysis any time and make changes if needed.
This app evaluates your driving style, climate control usage, driving in city versus open road and many other factors which influence costs and driving range. You will also get advice how to increase driving range and decrease costs!
